profile:
D. Roy Contracting company is based out of Ottawa, Ontario.
We have been in business for over a decade. 
We are an energetic team of general contractors with the goal to help improve the look and feel of your home. 
Our mission is to provide the best quality work in a timely fashion with an affordable price to ensure an all-around great customer experience. 
All jobs include a limited warranty because we stand behind what we do.

profile:
A family owned and operated business that is very efficient and professional.

We take pride in our work and get the job done right the first time.

We uphold a very good reputation for prompt service, fair pricing and professional results.

We do our utmost to maintain and protect your investment properly, whether it is a driveway or commercial parking lot.



We give back to our loyal repeat customers by offering several discounts.

We give you a $10 referral credit towards your next driveway seal for each paying customer that you send us in Our “Tell a friend” Referral Program.
We give you a $10 discount for group rates for three or more driveways sealed on the same street on the same day. “See Q & A for details.”
We guarantee to freeze the price of driveway sealing only, for up to 3 years, based on the price of oil remaining reasonably consistent. Starting in September 2007, our “Price Freeze Program” applies to any repeat customer who uses our services yearly without missing a year.


It is our goal that you to be satisfied with our services so that we can do business with you again next year.  Please call us for a free estimate and we will be more than happy to accommodate all of your asphalt and interlock needs.  We look forward to doing business with you and we thank you for your patronage!
services: Paving, interlock repair and installation and driveway sealing and repair
